將妻子送到急救室。不久，有醫護人員出來說，人已死亡。「所有在場家屬已經失去了思考能力，搶救人員拿出一張紙說：『這是搶救單子，你補簽一下』。」<br />\n延壯壯表示，從8月31日事發後至今，不但主診醫生和責任護士沒有露面給家屬一個解釋，連院方都沒有一個人站出來，給他們解釋和作出精神慰藉。他質問：「面對一屍兩命亡，誰該為生命負責？我們期待着真相！究竟是甚麼導致你（馬茸茸）摔下去？近11小時在五樓產房究竟發生了甚麼？醫生為甚麼拒絕剖腹產？為甚麼是沒有穿衣服墜樓？<span style=\"color: red;\">若是連死都不怕的人會害怕疼痛？</span>一個在產床上痛到半死的產婦身高1米61，挺着大肚子是如何爬上高達1.13米，寬為0.7米的窗台上墜樓的，即使產婦情緒失控要跳樓自殺，醫生，助產士，護士當時在幹甚麼？面對重重疑點，我們需要解釋。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170905/57171094\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170905%2F57171094&d=ExK9dujywAhJx97VqR7CPsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f38258e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170905%2F57171094&h=71121867\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170905/57171094</a></blockquote><br />\n到底邊個先真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n紅字個段咁似&quot;有勇氣自殺，點解無勇氣生存?&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲大陸人真係on99<br />\n屌你老母十大酷刑折磨你睇下你想唔想快啲死左佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n若是連死都不怕的人會害怕疼痛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f2355e9f9c6d57b1a4516f76fa894aec41c31d","tid":388094,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:31:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36c73b6550bf417bd71e8e670073c28c95889f07","tid":388094,"uid":76148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"DOUBLE KILL!"},{"pid":"41bdfc055eeadd1a34be69cd72437b2a23c79cf8","tid":388094,"uid":66381,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedB